Roadmap to version 0.0.3 :

- Port the GUI example to OCaml. This will develop the binding of the gui
namespace

- Complete the binding of SMaterial and allow rendering batches via IVideoDriver

- Bind SAnimatedMesh and add a few functions to SMeshBuffer

- In myocamlbuild.ml, make portable code for filenames (\ for windows)

- Allow the user to use a C++ compiler other than g++ via oasis and by
editing setup.ml
